summary: TWS: Telegraph Womens Sport - A Manifesto
title: TWS: Telegraph Womens Sport - A Manifesto
description:
sport, women, gender equality, representation

The Telegraph has launched the TWS - a platform spanning social media and with the support of contributors such as Judy Murray, Dina Asher-Smith and Jordan Nobbs. There will be a new monthly print supplement and integration of increased content into existing channels and sections.

Their manifesto states they will work to increase representation in the media, create dedicated products and channels, campaign on relevant issues, and grow the audience for women in sport.

I’m really excited.
